<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_c1cdd6fcf4ff.aspx"><b>小雅·瓠叶</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonc1cdd6fcf4ff">
<p>幡幡瓠叶，采之亨之。君子有酒，酌言尝之。</p>
<p>有兔斯首，炮之燔之。君子有酒，酌言献之。</p>
<p>有兔斯首，燔之炙之。君子有酒，酌言酢之。</p>
<p>有兔斯首，燔之炮之。君子有酒，酌言酬之。</p>
